    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only a few minor blemishes consistent with normal use, and the interior remains comfortable and in great shape. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a solid service history, making it a dependable choice for its next owner. You can expect a reliable driving experience with no major issues to address.",
