    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ideal for someone looking for a dependable daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior has some visible wear on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. Mechanically, it starts and runs reliably, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads and a tire rotation. Overall, it\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price of a showroom-ready model.",
