    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this truly pristine example. Maintained to the highest standards, this vehicle presents in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and a cabin that remains indistinguishable from new. Every detail, from the precision-engineered mechanicals to the meticulously preserved upholstery, reflects a history of uncompromising care. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a vehicle of unrivaled quality and lasting value.",
      "price": 46900.0,
