    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a world where time stands still. This isn't merely a vehicle; it is a symphony of steel and soul, finished in a hue that mirrors the midnight sky. Every stitch in the supple leather tells a story of meticulous care, and the wood grain glows with the warmth of a thousand sunsets. To sit behind the wheel is to command a masterpiece of engineering that breathes with a quiet, refined power. It has been preserved like a cherished memory, waiting for a driver who understands that true beauty is felt, not just seen. This is your invitation to own a legend that remains as breathtaking today as the day it first graced the open road.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
