      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This unit arrives in pristine, showroom-quality condition, having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure every mechanical and aesthetic detail meets our uncompromising standards. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior, this vehicle offers a like-new driving experience for the discerning enthusiast. We pride ourselves on transparency and quality; this is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example at a compelling value.",
